snippet: Bundesliga leaders Bayern Munich will be able to count on fit-again winger Arjen Robben when they host second-placed RB Leipzig on Wednesday in the final league match of the year, coach Carlo Ancelotti said on Tuesday....
lead_paragraph: Bundesliga leaders Bayern Munich will be able to count on fit-again winger Arjen Robben when they host second-placed RB Leipzig on Wednesday in the final league match of the year, coach Carlo Ancelotti said on Tuesday.

headline.main: Bayern Winger Robben Fit for Crunch Game Against Leipzig
headline.print_headline: Bayern Winger Robben Fit for Crunch Game Against Leipzig
